  "quest.00ABC6D5601DCD95.quest_desc": [
    "Every great angler knows that a fishing rod is only as good as its tackle.",
    "",
    "&6Hooks&r and &bBobbers&r can be attached to your rod to grant unique effects, from earning extra experience and treasure to making difficult catches easier or preserving your precious bait.",
    "",
    "Mix and match different combinations to suit your goals. Some attachments improve the fishing minigame, while others increase rewards or unlock entirely new possibilities, like &cCrystal Hooks&r for lava fishing.",
    "",
    "Experiment with different setups and find the perfect tackle for your next big catch. Sometimes, the right &6Hook&r or &bBobber&r is all that stands between an ordinary fish and a legendary haul.",
  ],
